---------------------------------------А      HELP for Configurator Sio2SD     А---------------------------------------А  Project by Jakub Kruszona-Zawadzki   А    firmware and pcb   (c) 2007-2011   АConfigurator by Pajero/MadTeam (c) 2011А---------------------------------------А  !=shift  ^=control  !^=shift+control А                                       А     1. BROWSING                       А  SPACE or JOY = page down selection  А !SPACE or JOY = page up selection    А        ^Q = home (first slot)         А        ^Z = end  (last slot)          А         = move files selection      А     JOY = move files selection      А   !^    = scroll files screen       А    ^    = scroll drives screen      А    !  = mode "M" as mapping drivesА    !    = mode "v" as -/+10 virtualsА                                       А     2. READING FILES                  А    RETURN long = set to D1 & ColdStartАRETURN (on dir) = enter to dir and readА            ESC = updir and read       А           ^ESC = root dir and read    А           LOGO = rewind dir and read  А            TAB = on/off read          А         !+.... = ...to back read      А             ^V = read all drives Vn   А                                       А     3. CHANGE MODE                    А       ^T = mode: Lcd/Mapping/Virtual  А     CAPS = on/off tracking read       А                                       А     4. MAPPING FILES                  А         1-8 = set drive 1-8           А         A-O = set drive 1-15          А       !+... = unset as -OFF-          А       ^+... = set at virtual drive    А     !Delete = undo last mapping       А          ^Y = change sing: 1-8 <-> A-HА     !^Clear = rebulding test all driveА                                       А     5. SELECT/EDIT MASK               А         = select mask 0 to 9        А       ^ = edition mask:             А             !DELETE = clear text      А                 ESC = escape          А              RETURN = only setup mask А LOGO or TAB (+shift)= setup and read  А                                       А     6. SWAP MODE                      А  ^S = swap, select two drives:        А        1-8 or A-O = mark drive        А               ESC = escape            А  plus all browsing keys...            А                                       А     7. FAVORITE/LAST USED             А       !; = add to favorite list       А        ; = enter to list:             А             ^P = on/off favorite      А         ^CLEAR = clear if not favoriteА            ESC = escape               АRETURN (on dir) = enter to dir and readА  plus all mapping and browsing keys   А                                       А     8. FIND FILES OR DIRS             А    ? = find equal set mask            А   !? = found,in file-goto his dir readА                                       А     9. WORKING AT ATR                 А    INSERT = create new empty ATR file:А   !INSERT = make dir:                 А         ESC = escape                  А      RETURN = only create/make        А        LOGO = create/make and read dirА    !+...... = ...to back read         АCLEAR = remove ATR (confirm Y/N)       А   ^R = rename ATR                     А                                       А     10. OTHERS                        А!^1 to !^4 = Sio2Sd number 1 to 4      А    X long = reboot, ColdStart         А        ^X = save setup and exit to dosА       !^S = save setup                А      HELP = listing this help         А     !HELP = new listing help          А--------------------------------end----А